snippet.title: Blocky Highway - Trailer (iOS / Android)
snippet.description:
AppStore: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/blocky-highway/id988750457
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dogbytegames.blockyrush

Blocky Highway is about racing traffic, avoiding trains, collecting cars and most importantly having fun. Open prize boxes to get new cars and complete collections! Drive at full speed to score big and be the #1. 

Key Features:
- Gorgeous voxel art graphics
- 30 different vehicles to drive (6 car collections to complete)
- 3 game modes
- 2 worlds to choose from
- Missions & Achievements
- Endless easy mode for Kids
- Crash Time
